WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.079 --> 00:00:04.648
welcome to the butchery fundamentals interactive&nbsp;app

00:00:04.648 --> 00:00:07.920
on this main page you'll find the instructions&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:07.920 --> 00:00:10.000
and the launch button

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.724
press the launch button to&nbsp;
open the application 

00:00:12.724 --> 00:00:14.320
when the application loads&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:14.320 --> 00:00:16.217
you'll find an interactive model

00:00:16.217 --> 00:00:18.217
press the start button to&nbsp;
begin

00:00:18.217 --> 00:00:20.186
the interactive model can be rotated

00:00:20.186 --> 00:00:21.481
and zoomed in on

00:00:21.481 --> 00:00:23.063
using&nbsp;the left mouse button

00:00:23.063 --> 00:00:25.063
and the scroll wheel

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:31.974
you will notice black and white tabs&nbsp;

00:00:31.974 --> 00:00:35.040
the black tabs will open sub-menus&nbsp;

00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:39.091
and allow you to explore different parts&nbsp;
of an animal

00:00:39.091 --> 00:00:42.976
clicking on any white tab will&nbsp;load a video on the right-hand side 

00:00:42.976 --> 00:00:46.080
press&nbsp;play on the video at the bottom left corner&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:46.080 --> 00:00:53.403
you can also maximize the video on the right&nbsp;
hand side and find closed captioning options

00:00:54.160 --> 00:00:58.000
the video specific glossary will&nbsp;
highlight any terms in the video&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:00.345
we want to bring to your attention

00:01:00.345 --> 00:01:05.275
other glossary&nbsp;terms can be found in the glossary of terms&nbsp;on the right hand side 

00:01:05.275 --> 00:01:12.000
this will open a separate&nbsp;
pop-up which you can leave open or close

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:18.240
to return to the entire animal protein locate&nbsp;
the back button at the top right corner of the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:18.301 --> 00:01:27.739
interactive window, to view all the videos in an&nbsp;
interactive menu click the view all videos button

00:01:33.440 --> 00:01:41.973
the reader button will provide verbal cues when&nbsp;
you roll over a particular item in the 3d menu

00:01:43.840 --> 00:01:49.193
any additional videos will be&nbsp;
located along the bottom bar

00:01:51.520 --> 00:01:57.280
beneath the video section will be a fax&nbsp;
and interesting information media section&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:58.080 --> 00:02:02.443
each media item will have a title listed below the picture

00:02:03.450 --> 00:02:06.619
click on the picture to review the&nbsp;related information

00:02:07.646 --> 00:02:10.794
clicking the x button will&nbsp;
close the menu

00:02:10.794 --> 00:02:12.400
at the bottom of the page

00:02:12.400 --> 00:02:15.124
you will find a start quiz button

00:02:15.124 --> 00:02:18.800
press this button&nbsp;when you are comfortable and ready to take a quiz&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:18.800 --> 00:02:20.989
on the subject matter you've just studied

00:02:20.989 --> 00:02:26.502
if at any time you are lost you can press the butchery fundamentals icon 

00:02:26.502 --> 00:02:31.840
to return to the&nbsp;
splash page or starting point of the application&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:31.840 --> 00:02:37.123
you are now ready to explore the app and the&nbsp;
various content features that are available

